strings.Value: "Wait a bit. I have something to do first."
{n}Entering the capital, Octavia and Regongar come up to you. The half-elf leans over to your ear and whispers, biting it tenderly,{/n} "I want you."
{n}Regongar kisses your neck and whispers into the other ear,{/n} "Right now."
{n}Taking you tenderly by the arms, the couple almost runs with you to the palace.{/n}
"Ha, Your Highness... Since when is love not a matter of national importance?"
